== Deaths == * [[元豊 (宋)|元豊]] 8th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1085]] {{ill|April 1|ja|4月1日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Emperor Shenzong (Song)|ja|神宗|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 6th Emperor of the Song dynasty (born [[1048]]). * {{ill|Bunkyū|ja|文久|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1861]] {{ill|April 14|ja|4月14日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Utagawa Kuniyoshi|ja|歌川国芳|12=draft|12=draft}}, a renowned ukiyo-e artist (born [[1797]]).
