régorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft}} [[1714]] {{ill|April 18|ja|4月18日|12=draft}}) – The senior retainer of Ōoku, {{ill|Eshima|ja|絵島|12=draft}}, was exiled to Takato in Shinshū following punishment in the 【Ejima Ikushima Incident|江島生島事件】. * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|12=draft|12=draft}} 11th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft}} [[1840]] {{ill|April 7|ja|4月7日|12=draft}}) – The 7th-generation kabuki actor {{ill|Ichikawa Danjūrō (7th)|ja|市川團十郎 (7代目)|12=draft}} gave the first performance of one of kabuki’s 18 repertoire pieces, “{{ill|Kanjin-chō|ja|勧進帳|12=draft}}.”
== Births == * [[Ryakuō]] 3rd year / [[興国]] 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft}} [[1340]] {{ill|April 2|ja|4月2日|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Ashikaga Mototada|ja|足利基氏|12=draft}}, the second son of {{ill|Ashikaga Takauji|ja|足利尊氏|12=draft}}, and the first Kamakura Kubō (died [[1367]]). * [[永正]] 8th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft}} [[1511]] {{ill|April 2|ja|4月2日|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Ashikaga Yoshiharu|ja|足利義晴|12=draft}}, the 12th shōgun of the Ashikaga Shogunate (died [[1550]]). * [[Meiji era|Meiji]] 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft}} [[1869]] {{ill|April 16|ja|4月16日|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Kawakami Bēzan|ja|川上眉山|12=draft}}, a novelist (died [[1908]]).
== Deaths == * [[元豊 (宋)|元豊]] 8th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft}} [[1085]] {{ill|April 1|ja|4月1日|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Emperor Shenzong (Song)|ja|神宗|12=draft}}, the 6th Emperor of the Song dynasty (born [[1048]]). * {{ill|Bunkyū|ja|文久|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft}} [[1861]] {{ill|April 14|ja|4月14日|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Utagawa Kuniyoshi|ja|歌川国芳|12=draft}}, a renowned ukiyo-e artist (born [[1797]]).
