* {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} 8th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1580]] _月_日) – {{ill|Oda Nobunaga|ja|織田信長|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} reached a peace agreement with Ishiyama Hongan-ji; as a result, {{ill|Kōsa|ja|高佐|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} withdrew from Ishiyama, effectively ending the 【Ishiyama Campaign|石山合戦】.
* [[正徳 (日本)|正徳]] 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1714]] {{ill|April 18|ja|4月18日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}) – The senior retainer of Ōoku, {{ill|Eshima|ja|絵島|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}, was exiled to Takato in Shinshū following punishment in the 【Ejima Ikushima Incident|江島生島事件】.
* {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} 11th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1840]] {{ill|April 7|ja|4月7日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}) – The 7th-generation kabuki actor {{ill|Ichikawa Danjūrō (7th)|ja|市川團十郎 (7代目)|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} gave the first performance of one of kabuki’s 18 repertoire pieces, “{{ill|Kanjin-chō|ja|勧進帳|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}.”

== Births ==
* [[Ryakuō]] 3rd year / [[興国]] 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1340]] {{ill|April 2|ja|4月2日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Ashikaga Mototada|ja|足利基氏|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}, the second son of {{ill|Ashikaga Takauji|ja|足利尊氏|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}, and the first Kamakura Kubō (died [[1367]]).
* [[永正]] 8th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1511]] {{ill|April 2|ja|4月2日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Ashikaga Yoshiharu|ja|足利義晴|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 12th shōgun of the Ashikaga Shogunate (died [[1550]]).
* [[Meiji era|Meiji]] 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1869]] {{ill|April 16|ja|4月16日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Kawakami Bēzan|ja|川上眉山|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}, a novelist (died [[1908]]).

== Deaths ==
* [[元豊 (宋)|元豊]] 8th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1085]] {{ill|April 1|ja|4月1日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Emperor Shenzong (Song)|ja|神宗|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 6th Emperor of the Song dynasty (born [[1048]]).
