== Births == * [[Ryakuō]] 3rd year / [[興国]] 1st year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1340|1340]] [[:en:April 2|April 2]]) – [[:en:Ashikaga Motouji|Ashikaga Mototada]], the second son of [[:en:Ashikaga Takauji|Ashikaga Takauji]], and the first Kamakura Kubō (died [[:en:1367|1367]]). * [[永正]] 8th year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1511|1511]] [[:en:April 2|April 2]]) – [[:en:Ashikaga Yoshiharu|Ashikaga Yoshiharu]], the 12th shōgun of the Ashikaga Shogunate (died [[1550]]). * [[Meiji era|Meiji]] 2nd year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[1869]] [[:en:April 16|April 16]]) – [[:en:Bizan Kawakami|Kawakami Bēzan]], a novelist (died [[1908]]).
== Deaths == * [[元豊 (宋)|元豊]] 8th year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1085|1085]] [[:en:April 1|April 1]]) – [[:en:Thần Tông|Emperor Shenzong (Song)]], the 6th Emperor of the Song dynasty (born [[:en:1048|1048]]). * [[:en:Bunkyū|Bunkyū]] 1st year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[1861]] [[:en:April 14|April 14]]) – [[:en:Utagawa Kuniyoshi|Utagawa Kuniyoshi]], a renowned ukiyo-e artist (born [[1797]]).
